            <title>PS5 新专利：重返旧时剧情，玩家透过触发点回带游戏重要时刻</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/14/content-streaming-with-gameplay-launch/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=content-streaming-with-gameplay-launch</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/14/content-streaming-with-gameplay-launch/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Christy]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 11:26:44 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Content Streaming With Gameplay Launch]]>
