            <title>WhatsApp 新群组「语音对话」    可一 group 人语音倾偈 + 只弹讯息提醒</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/14/whatsapp-17/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=whatsapp-17</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/14/whatsapp-17/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[EMMA]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 11:19:02 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣闻]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1204560</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>通讯平台 WhatsApp 宣布，已正式向用户推出全新「语音对话（Voice Chat）」功能，让用户以全新的方式与大型群组中的其他成员保持实时联系。</p><p>与 WhatsApp 年前推出的「群组语音通话（Group Voice Call）」相比，群组内的成员在新的语音聊天功能中只会收到推送通知，而不是直接收到来电。成员可以自行选择是否加入对话，以减低干扰。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">rolling out now: voice chat for your larger groups!</p><p>you’ll soon have the option to talk it out live with whoever can join or keep texting with whoever can’t</p><p>&mdash; WhatsApp (@WhatsApp) <a href="https://twitter.com/WhatsApp/status/1724124816532177123?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">November 13, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>而在语音聊天期间，用户可以从聊天顶部方便地存取呼叫控制项，包括取消静音、自行挂断通话等，不会妨碍参与者同时发送文字讯息的能力，与 Discord、Telegram 和 Slack 上的功能类似。</p><blockquote><p><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/11/11/whatsapp-ads-are-coming/software/android-app/">WhatsApp 高层确认，将会在程式内加入广告</a></p><p>&#8211;</p><p><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/11/08/whatsapp-mac-app-store/software/mac-app/">Mac 版真原生 WhatsApp 程式，推出 3 个月终于 AppStore 登陆</a></p></blockquote><p>新功能受 WhatsApp 以端对端加密，以保护用户的讯息、语音、通话内容等资料不会外泄至第三方。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1204568 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-14-16.23.46-694x387.png" alt="" width="694" height="387" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-14-16.23.46-694x387.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-14-16.23.46-768x429.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-14-16.23.46.png 1168w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" />（图片来源：<a href="https://techcrunch.com/2023/11/13/whatsapp-launches-new-discord-like-voice-chat-feature-large-groups/">techcrunch</a>）</p><p>日前 WhatsApp 正陆续在全球 iOS 和 Android 平台上推出新功能，并会先让拥有 33 名至 128 名成员的大型群组使用，预料日后会扩展至其他较细规模的群组。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://techcrunch.com/2023/11/13/whatsapp-launches-new-discord-like-voice-chat-feature-large-groups/">techcrunch</a>、<a href="https://www.businesstoday.in/technology/news/story/whatsapps-new-feature-unveiled-check-out-the-new-way-to-voice-chat-with-large-groups-405631-2023-11-14">businesstoday</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

